  <brief_title>PK Study of T-817 in Subjects With Hepatic Impairment</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1, Two-Part, Open-Label, Parallel-Cohort, Single-Dose Study to Determine the Pharmacokinetics of T-817MA in Adult Subjects With Hepatic Impairment and in Healthy Adult Subjects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
